<BaseLayout
  title="Painting & Finishes | Professional Interior & Exterior Services in Venezuela"
  description="Expert painting services, decorative finishes, and microcement applications. Transform your spaces with premium materials and flawless execution in Valencia, San Diego and Caracas."
